---
title: Chicken & Roast Veggie Dhal with Garlic Tortilla Chips & Yoghurt
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour. Here,
we're adding tender pieces of chicken, sweet roasted kumara and carrot, and crunchy garlic flatbread chips.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-sweet-potato-dhal-5455d84f.jpg
